# personal_info_form()`} 
                />
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-700 rounded-lg p-4 mt-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-300">Solution Hints</h4>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                  <li>Use <code>input()</code> to collect name, age, and email</li>
                  <li>Convert age to an integer if needed</li>
                  <li>Use f-strings for formatted output</li>
                  <li>Consider input validation</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </li>
            
            <li>
              <strong>Calculator App:</strong> Build a simple calculator that takes two numbers and an operation as input, then displays the result.
              <div class="mt-4">
                <CodePlayground 
                  client:load 
                  initialCode={`# Calculator App Challenge
